HEADWORD: Bogtrotter
<hw>Bog"trot`ter</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who lives
in a boggy country; -- applied in derision to the lowest class of
Irish.</def> <rj><au>Halliwell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
